    <div id="Overview" class="tab-pane fade in active">
            <p>The main objective of the Beyond GDP Sprint is to probe the <q> Inclusive Wealth</q> approach to measuring well-being 
                by identifying generally agreed areas of high priority for research and, where possible, agree on common frameworks.
            </p>
            <p>The meeting on Modern Capital will discuss the scope of modern capitals (including intangible capital, human capital, 
                natural capital, etc.) and how to consistently measure these  modern capitals and their resultant flows of benefits.
